<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Admin Panel</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #eee;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .admin-panel {
            background: rgba(255,0,0,0.1);
            border: 2px solid #ff4444;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        h1 { color: #ff4444; }
        .bypass-info {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        code {
            background: #000;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            color: #4ecdc4;
        }
        .user-info {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="admin-panel">
        <h1>üîí Admin Panel</h1>

        <div class="user-info">
            <p><strong>Logged in as:</strong> <%= user.username %></p>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> <%= user.role %></p>
        </div>

        <h2>Admin Functions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/api/v1/users" style="color: #4ecdc4;">View All Users</a></li>
            <li><a href="/config" style="color: #4ecdc4;">System Configuration</a></li>
            <li><a href="/debug" style="color: #4ecdc4;">Debug Information</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bypass-info">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è VULNERABILITY: Broken Access Control</h3>
            <p>This "admin" check only looks at a client-side cookie!</p>
            <p>To bypass, set this cookie in your browser:</p>
            <code>auth={"username":"admin","role":"admin"}</code>

            <h4 style="margin-top: 15px;">Using curl:</h4>
            <code>curl -b 'auth={"username":"admin","role":"admin"}' http://localhost:3000/admin</code>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><a href="/" style="color: #4ecdc4;">‚Üê Back to Home</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
